们面临全球贸易战还有一个更重要的原因，那就是中国对经济放缓的反应。</p><h4>中国正在利用出口过剩来应对经济放缓</h4><p>占中国经济四分之一以上的房地产业已经基本崩溃，导致中国的大部分内需也随之下降。在这种环境下，一个明显的举措就是努力提振出口制造业。</p><p>只要看一眼中国的银行在哪里发放贷款就可以清楚地看出，这正是中国正在做的事情： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1547b4ad-9edc-4463-8d9e-1ed2e91d8ff9_1092x1200.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1547b4ad-9edc-4463-8d9e-1ed2e91d8ff9_1092x1200.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1547b4ad-9edc-4463-8d9e-1ed2e91d8ff9_1092x1200.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1547b4ad-9edc-4463-8d9e-1ed2e91d8ff9_1092x1200.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1547b4ad-9edc-4463-8d9e-1ed2e91d8ff9_1092x1200.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1547b4ad-9edc-4463-8d9e-1ed2e91d8ff9_1092x1200.jpeg" width="642" height="705.4945054945055" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1547b4ad-9edc-4463-8d9e-1ed2e91d8ff9_1092x1200.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot