hpinion.blog/p/a-vote-for-trump-is-a-vote-for-chaos">唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）是混乱的代理人</a>，而且<a href="https://twitter.com/ArmandDoma/status/1752857671970242636">每天</a>似乎<a href="https://twitter.com/niubi/status/1752727513363579360">都在提醒人们</a><a href="https://twitter.com/GregTSargent/status/1752672012584022493">这一事实</a>。但是，美国人不喜欢投票支持两种邪恶中的小事 - 他们会想听听拜登为何积极好事。</p><p>这可能很棘手；我看过候选人选择错误的消息的情况。最值得注意的是，我记得2000年的阿尔·戈尔（Al Gore）试图向“ <a href="https://slate.com/news-and-politics/2002/08/al-gore-s-bogus-defense-of-his-populist-message.html">人民与强者</a>”的左民人们传达。对于曾担任副总统八年繁荣的候选人来说，这是一个非常奇怪的选择。首先，普通美国人在经济上比以往任何时候都做得更好，为什么他们会心情兴奋地将颠覆性的阶级冲突引入方程式中？似乎是一种“停留”类型的信息，就像乔治·HW Bush在1988年使用的那样，它本来会变得更聪明。其次，如果2000年是推出民粹主义十字军东征的时候，为什么阿尔·戈尔（Al Gore）在过去的八年中没有这样做？无论如何，对于戈尔来说，它似乎并不是很好。</p><p>我认为拜登可能会犯有类似的错误。他对以色列的支持使许多左倾的年轻人对他生气（在<a href="https://twitter.com/micsolana/status/1752718669782642810">Tiktok的一点协助</a>下）。解决这一弱点的一种方法是拥抱一些剩下的年轻人喜欢的事情，例如对气候政策的左派立场。在我看来，这将是一个错误。</p><h4>拜登给了我们更便宜的能量，并在此过程中对气候变化造成了打击</h4><p>大多数左派气候活动家，包括日出运动，灭绝叛乱，格雷塔·敦伯格（Greta Thunberg）等，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/our-climate-change-debates-are-out">在2010年或更早的世界中仍然非常精神陷入困境</a>。在这个世界观中，只有富裕世界人民的消费减少和惩罚性减少才能避免灾难性的全球灾难。很久以前，这可能是真的，但今天是纯粹的幻想。首先，发达国家作为与中国和亚洲其他地区的全球碳排放量<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/annual-co2-emissions-per-country?time=1850..latest&amp;country=CHN~USA~OWID_EUR~Asia+%28excl.+China+and+India%29">迅速缩小</a>（不，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/no-the-us-didnt-outsource-our-carbon">这不是因为外包</a>）。</p><p>但更重要的是，技术的重大变化意味着世界不再面临保持现代生活水平和拯救气候免于灾难的选择。廉价的太阳能和电池每年仍在越来越便宜 -<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/our-climate-change-debates-are-out">完全改变了方程式</a>。我们不再面临丰富和气候稳定之间的选择 - 由于廉价的绿色能源，这些目标现在是一个又一个。</p><p>气候旺克和能量旺克斯意识到了这一事实。企业也是如此；这就是为什么德克萨斯州是一个深红色州，现在已经超过了太阳能的加利福尼亚。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg" width="1456" height="817" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:817,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:64035,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/NatBullard/status/1716794734105203000">纳特·布拉德</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>德克萨斯州还可以<a href="https://www.houstonchronicle.com/business/energy/article/ercot-grid-battery-solar-enel-texas-18350609.php">通过电池存储为前进</a>。</p><p>如果太阳能是一种经济效率低下，昂贵的能源形式，那就<em>不会发生</em>这种情况。如果这样做代表经济牺牲或生活水平的降低，德克萨斯人绝不会在庞大的剪辑中建造太阳能。 Ergo，因此，太阳能并不是使我们贫穷的事情。太阳能和电池意味着能源丰度 - 这意味着美国人<em>会消耗更多，而不是更少</em>。他们为自己的房屋获得便宜的电力，从太阳能脱盐的淡化中获得便宜的水，依此类推。</p><p><em>这</em>是我认为拜登需要的气候信息。由于某种原因，他的标志性气候政策被称为“减少通货膨胀法”。这个想法是，太阳能和风能的便宜电力将降低公司的成本，从而降低通货膨胀。爱尔兰共和军可能还没有采取任何措施来降低通货膨胀，但是他们给它起了这个名字的事实表明，民主党人将其视为一种<em>能源丰富的政策</em>。因此，一个很好的信息是，我们为美国人带来了更便宜，更丰富的电力，同时还可以在此过程中与气候变化作斗争。</p><p><a href="https://www.slowboring.com/p/climate-is-the-problem">马特·伊格利亚斯（Matt Yglesias）在最近的一篇文章中认为</a>，拜登（Biden）应该完全关注一般廉价能源的信息，而不是特别是气候变化：</p><blockquote><p>拜登（Biden）颁布了<em>迄今为止</em>美国历史上任何总统最重要的气候政策……[但是]拜登和民主党人应该无情地对能量进行三角态度，吹嘘他们成功的全能[能源]政策，基本上永远不会提及气候改变，不制定任何以气候为中心的新政策。</p></blockquote><p>我认为这个建议有优点。例如，拜登（Biden）应该绝对吹牛，因为他帮助我们将石油生产提高到了历史最高水平： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg" width="970" height="647" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:647,&quot;width&quot;:970,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:36787,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.eia.gov/dnav/pet/hist/LeafHandler.ashx?n=PET&amp;s=MCRFPUS2&amp;f=M">环境影响评估</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>正如<a href="https://washingtonmonthly.com/2023/03/07/joe-biden-broke-his-2020-pledge-on-fracking-good/">比尔·谢尔（Bill Scher）一年前在《华盛顿月刊》中报道的</a>那样，其中许多确实是拜登（Biden）的工作：</p><blockquote><p>拜登上任后，他的政府继续发行石油和天然气许可证，并以比他的前任唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump） <a href="https://news.yahoo.com/biden-granted-more-oil-and-gas-drilling-permits-than-trump-in-his-first-2-years-in-office-190528616.html">更快的速度</a>。去年签署的《卫生保健与能源法案》（这项笨拙的<a href="https://www.naturalgasintel.com/why-is-inflation-reduction-act-a-big-deal-for-natural-gas-oil-industries/">通货膨胀降低法案</a>）Yokeok and ok and of the墨西哥湾和阿拉斯加厨师入口处的油气租赁拍卖，并祝福在联邦土地上的风和太阳能项目。</p></blockquote><p>这使汽油价格降低。现在的汽油比十年前便宜，而且相对于平均工资，它便宜<em>得多</em>： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F182abf01-e110-46cb-a9c0-a213497eb9cd_1318x450.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F182abf01-e110-46cb-a9c0-a213497eb9cd_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F182abf01-e110-46cb-a9c0-a213497eb9cd_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F182abf01-e110-46cb-a9c0-a213497eb9cd_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F182abf01-e110-46cb-a9c0-a213497eb9cd_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2